q(201,"¿Cuántos profetas se mencionan por nombre en el Corán?","How many prophets are mentioned by name in the Quran?","شحال من نبي مذكور بالاسم فالقرآن؟",["20","25","28","30"],["20","25","28","30"],["20","25","28","30"],"25","25","25","Profetas","medium","El Corán menciona 25 profetas por nombre, aunque los eruditos creen que Allah envió 124,000 profetas en total.","The Quran mentions 25 prophets by name, although scholars believe Allah sent 124,000 prophets in total.","القرآن كيذكر 25 نبي بالاسم، وخا العلماء كيعتقدو أن الله بعث 124,000 نبي فالمجموع."),
q(202,"¿Cuántos profetas se mencionan en el Corán que recibieron libros sagrados?","How many prophets mentioned in the Quran received holy books?","شحال من نبي مذكور فالقرآن تعطاه كتاب مقدس؟",["2","3","4","5"],["2","3","4","5"],["2","3","4","5"],"4","4","4","Profetas","hard","Cuatro profetas recibieron libros sagrados: Musa (Tawrah), Dawud (Zabur), Isa (Injil) y Muhammad (Corán).","Four prophets received holy books: Musa (Tawrah), Dawud (Zabur), Isa (Injil), and Muhammad (Quran).","أربعة أنبياء تعطاوهم كتب مقدسة: موسى (التوراة)، داوود (الزبور)، عيسى (الإنجيل)، و محمد (القرآن)."),
