q(204,"¿Cuál fue el milagro principal del Profeta Dawud (David)?","What was the main miracle of Prophet Dawud (David)?","أشنو كانت المعجزة الرئيسية ديال النبي داوود؟",["Hablar con animales","Ablandar el hierro con sus manos","Dividir el mar","Curar enfermos"],["Speaking with animals","Softening iron with his hands","Splitting the sea","Healing the sick"],["الهضرة مع الحيوانات","تليين الحديد بيديه","شق البحر","شفاء المرضى"],"Ablandar el hierro con sus manos","Softening iron with his hands","تليين الحديد بيديه","Profetas","hard","Allah ablandó el hierro para el Profeta Dawud, permitiéndole hacer armaduras con sus propias manos.","Allah softened iron for Prophet Dawud, allowing him to make armor with his own hands.","الله لين الحديد للنبي داوود، و خلاه يصنع الدروع بيديه."),
